      Kubernetes, Vue, GraphQL, Golang, and much more. It's built with Gatsby,
      CircleCI for CI/CD, and Terraform.
    </p>
    <p>
      Please make a pull request if you want to fix a bug or suggest a feature.
      The{" "}
      <a href="https://github.com/harrisoncramer/harrisoncramer.me">
        repository
      </a>{" "}
      is on Github.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  h2 {
    @apply my-4;
  }
  p {
    @apply my-2;
  }
</style>
